inquiries.query:
/*
In the job postings fact table get the job id, job title short, job location, job via, and salary year avg columns.
Only return 'Full-Time' jobs (hint: look at the job_schedule_type column).

*/

SELECT
	job_id,
    job_title_short,
    job_location,
    job_via,
    salary_year_avg
	
FROM 
	job_postings_fact
where 
	job_schedule_type = 'Full-time'
inquiries.name: com practice problem-2
